## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not fully capture the diversity of perspectives across different societies. Additionally, the search was constrained by the availability of online resources and the specificity of search terms. Further research could include a broader range of cultural contexts and academic studies to provide a more comprehensive understanding.

